Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.12,0:00:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}避難通道在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}優先低年級學生避難
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.33,0:00:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請大家遵從學生會的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.72,0:00:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要推擠 不要說話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.37,0:00:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快點 這裡馬上要封閉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}展開防壁的準備已經完成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.36,0:00:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以展開防壁了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.53,0:00:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有沒有沒趕上避難的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}封死防壁 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行 無法掌握魔獸的數量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.64,0:00:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}居然能無限增加
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果魔獸來自預設的魔法陣 那麼在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.83,0:00:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼 在這裡展開防壁會斷了退路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很快就會被突破
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.02,0:00:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還需要補充魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣下去無法統計避難人數 重來一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}我們無法和別的班共享資訊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}竟把我們逼到這種境地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看來魔獸確實是從學校內部湧出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}受傷人數超出預計
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.45,0:00:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}首先我們必須穩住陣腳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.89,0:00:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}辦公樓完全陷落了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們這麼弱的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}由於敵人重點攻擊學生集中的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:01:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}導致初始防線完全失去意義
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.88,0:01:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做好記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.72,0:01:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會長 西南門已經撐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.68,0:01:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很快將會侵入南樓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.37,0:01:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}防壁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.23,0:01:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}防衛班在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}全員負傷 無法維持防壁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}必須盡可能讓更多的人避難
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.45,0:01:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}南樓失去聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}誰能過去確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.50,0:01:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}應該還有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.86,0:01:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}沒有多餘人手了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}首先應該展開防壁 然後實施救援
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.28,0:01:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會長 西南門已被攻陷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}醫務樓確認敵人入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對方請求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.12,0:01:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會長！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道該去哪裡避難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.54,0:02:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快去避難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.96,0:02:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.88,0:02:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請不要忘記自己的立場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.67,0:02:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起 安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.23,0:02:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼 為什麼只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒想到醫務樓會陷落
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}裡面的學生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:02:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}預備的醫療物資呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去確認
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剩下的全部搬到大講堂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}校園內還有多少學生沒來得及撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然不知道準確數量 還有不少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個時候公主殿下會怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被狠狠地上了一課
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大講堂已經被占領了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}我去確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}不要離開自己的崗位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收集物資
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}防衛班已被擊潰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}由於防壁消失 預計魔獸將會入侵這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}避難工作還沒完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.47,0:03:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救援呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在過去會被捲進去的 保持鎮定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會長 我們應該派救援過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}你的意思是要我們放任不管嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}可是去送死是沒有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}傳令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在派人過去 也只是徒增傷亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要拋棄他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放棄西樓 同樣也放棄這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家各自帶上必要的物品前往橋門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼請立即在主樓梯展開防壁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣一來 等於是失去了半個校園
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}主樓梯處的防壁看來是有效了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}目前主樓仍在堅守
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道還能有多少人成功逃來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去西門那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能派些人來支援圖書館嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明大家都在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請您務必尊重大家的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這不公平 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有這麼多學生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了 原來你沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起 我沒能守住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.07,0:05:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有我們能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也想為我們出力的 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}臣願一同前往
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請按顏色分開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}注意保持隊形
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們去橋門前迎戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}盡全力牽制住敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不惜一切代價 一定要把魔獸困在學院內部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做好關閉橋門的準備了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已經完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快點 大家快點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抓緊時間 馬上就要關門了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從沒見過這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:06:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會長她們沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}公…公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在哪在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}公主殿下 為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 你要對古蕾婭做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}粗蠻之輩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Schweinshaxe！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪裡很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3} 那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}停止訓練 停止訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.41,0:09:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他說停止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.51,0:09:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.95,0:09:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽說是巨像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個能修好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}避難演習到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}估計不能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}除負責修復的學生請立即前往通信樓集合後放學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}重播一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.18,0:09:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 公主殿下不能掌握一下分寸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果公主殿下只是在一邊看著的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}校園不至於被破壞成這副模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我才叮囑安不要出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}漢娜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}關於這次避難演習的應對措施
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}問題果然出在混亂的指揮系統
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了應對不測 需要作出準確的取捨決定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}首先防衛線的布置就有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道不應該首先確保通向橋門的避難通道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.79,0:10:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還能修好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}估計不能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能暫時放假了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}---------------next------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Manaria Friends 第六話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}浮於海面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以決定舉行一次僅由學生主導的避難訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽起來很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}具體的訓練內容是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了防範針對學院的魔獸侵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:12:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}引導所有學生通過橋門前往通信樓避難
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}魔獸的替身由老師負責製造
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們會造很多出來 要打起精神防衛好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最近都沒能全力使用魔法 我已經躍躍欲試了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無論什麼敵人都不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遇上我全部一擊搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}公主殿下 關於這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這次希望公主殿下在一旁參觀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}參觀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這次訓練說到底只是針對學生的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請公主殿下不要參加
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果公主參加了 學生們會過分依靠公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不少人認為這樣一來就失去了訓練的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不不不 可以依靠我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是安的魔力實在太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能連同校園一鍋端了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:12:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才不會破壞校園呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}學生會也一致認為
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這次訓練應該僅由我們學生完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我也是學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不會妨礙大家的 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}公主殿下 到時請您務必不要插手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不需要你的協助哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對了 古蕾婭作為迎擊班參加訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的 我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好羨慕 我也想參加訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,
